<Author>Dan022
<Content>Loved this Hotel Stayed here in May 08, and had a fantastic time. We arrived very late and were given a very small room (which for a night or two, would be ok), we came straight back down and were moved the following day...no problems.The staff were fantastic, the guys on recepton could'nt do enough for us - very friendly. The hotel is a little further back, from the very centre of Barcelona, but is no more than a pleasant 20 min stroll, or just round the corner was a tube stop.This is only a small hotel so has quiet a nice feel to it, there is a bar but was not always open.FAB hotel for people that will be out exploring Barcelona. When we went this hotel was much better value than other similar standard hotels. 
