<Author>tziambra
<Content>Great value in Barcelona We stayed at tehe NH Master for a weekend in December. It was not my first time in Barcelona and I have stayed at other hotels. I really liked the NH Master because it is central but not in the middle of the very touristic areas, so it is a bit quieter. It is a nice walk through the residential area towards the Plaza Catalunya or the Passeig de Gracia. The rooms are simple and modern and the bathroom is large and clean, I always enjoy the little shampoos and toiletries they have for free. The price is great compared to more expenisive hotels I stayed at before and were not as nice. 
