<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Very convenient hotel close to the city centre I really enjoyed our stay at NH Master. The rooms are quite large, immaculate, with wooden flooring and modern furnishing. The bathroom was big and extremely clean. This is a fairly large hotel which may seem a little bit anonymous, but staff was generally friendly and helpful. The hotel is about 7 minutes walk from the nearest underground station, otherwise it is possible to walk to the Ramblas in about 20/30 minutes. All in all, a very clean hotel close to the city centre. 
